  "title": "Structural Design Engineer",
  "description": "<ul><li>Design of viaduct layouts and tendon details</li><li>Draft construction design drawings for viaduct structure and submission for approval</li><li>Generate BBS (bar bending schedule)</li><li>Revision of drawings as per comments/instructions of the client</li><li>Reports progress and performance to the Senior Engineer and Design Manager</li><li>Monitor and update design schedule regularly</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor's Degree in Civil Engineering or Equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years of experience in design of construction of bridge or viaduct or roads or highways</li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
